name: New World Order
description: The New World Order coin is a deflationary token built on Binance Smartchain, also referred to as the ‘Elite Coin’ among the community. The New World Order coin is set to be the totalisation of Financial Systems. NEWOs will be a store of value, a medium of transaction, and a hedge against inflation.Community event 2021 -693 Billion Coins(99%) were burnt.NEWO road map will signify 100% automation and decentralisation when they achieve their final Target of being Listed at the Binance Exchange.
